    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deep in the never-changing autumn, surrounded by the tall buildings of the city. Men in suits move like shadows between the asphalt bridges. Can the songs of their childhood and the sweet taste of a drink make them forget the lies they find in a melancholic sunset?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A short almost-linear novel game written for the common man.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Reading time of 5-10 mins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Almost no sounds, or music. Disturbing noise loops.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Graphics picturing the loud emptiness of a city full of people.</p>",
